text: Muskeg River is a settlement in northern Alberta, Canada within the Municipal District of Greenview No. 16. ==Geography== It is located at the junction of the Bighorn Highway (Highway 40) and Forestry Trunk Road (former Highway 734), approximately east of Grande Cache. It has an elevation of . Muskeg River flows through the community and north into the Smoky River. == See also == *List of communities in Alberta *List of settlements in Alberta == References == Category:Localities in the Municipal District of Greenview No. 16
title: Muskeg River, Alberta
